{"tid":296751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[悲情城市一日三跳]翔龍灣女子墮樓 倒斃泳池邊","createTime":"2017-06-25T00:07:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-25T11:19:33.000Z","uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b0afc9b7ef1879f0e796a6ec0fec82b498ad3b57","tid":296751,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T00:07:57.000Z","msg":"土瓜灣新碼頭街38號翔龍灣，早上約6時56分，一名約30多歲女子從高處墮下，倒臥平台泳池旁邊。救護員接報到場，證實已經死亡。警方調查事件原因。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170625/56872765\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170625%2F56872765&d=fZFS8tXsTIlra8mgLvL2fP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=5d65b687\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170625%2F56872765&h=61cc6bfd\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170625/56872765</a>"},{"pid":"9ff5adb68ac77b37cd5105c0aeb27fe678b01480","tid":296751,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T00:09:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170625/large/1498348846_2359.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170625%2Flarge%2F1498348846_2359.jpg&h=d9d7a5c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名男子協助警方調查。深灣游艇會對開山邊，途人發現4隻野豬徘徊，於是報警。警員接報到場，發現只有3隻約1米長小野豬，在山邊翻垃圾相信到來覓食，警員驅趕但並不成功。警員從旁戒備，並通知漁護署人員到場處理。(黎志偉攝)<br />\n<br />\n蘋果做乜鳩 貼錯相?<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.news.ebc.net.tw/images/2017/05/05/149397168373560x6eebyS1u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.news.ebc.net.tw%2Fimages%2F2017%2F05%2F05%2F149397168373560x6eebyS1u.jpg&h=9e9599f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fcb4a1e4b7b56be4342618f23ff6afb80d351764","tid":296751,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T00:09:38.000Z","msg":"又開始了"},{"pid":"dc540f8916468edfb32c8c0ba94363068b9e1b89","t